"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据共同社当地时间 1 月 25 日消息，在日本长崎县男女群岛以西 110 公里的海上，香港籍货轮「JINTIAN」沉没。 日本第 7 管区海上保安总部称，船上有 22 名船员，包括 14 名中国人和 8 名缅甸人，其中 5 人被附近正在航行的民间船只救助，获救者中至少有 4 人是中国船员，其余 17 人可能乘坐救生艇在海上漂流，海保正在加紧搜索。 来自民间船只的信息显示，船员转移到救生艇上，货轮已沉没。 报道称，24 日晚上 11 点 15 分左右，该货轮发出求救信号。日本第 7 管区表示，接到该货轮的卫星电话称「船已倾斜浸水」。 另据韩联社报道，据韩国济州海警 25 日消息，该货轮当天凌晨 1 点 45 分许在济州道西归浦市东南方向 148.2 公里的韩日中间海域航行途中沉没。 韩国济州海警厅目前正在事故现场与日本海上保安厅联动救助船员。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ed2397cb2d364c9885b8b32cd073d68d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "19 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/580427173"}}, "attached_info": "ClUI89ekpL/MpOREEAMaCDkxMjY1NzI0IMi4wp4GMAc4qQFAHnIJNTgwNDI3MTczeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "31_1674652533.676539", "card_id": "Q_580060954", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 28}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《流浪地球 2》里的各版 550 智能量子计算机离现实有多远？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-92494fc7f9f718f6380c4210587b70fb_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "16 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/580060954"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I89ekpL/MpOREEAMaCDkxMTg0MTUwILnbtJ4GMAc4c0Afcgk1ODAwNjA5NTR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "32_1674652533.676949", "card_id": "Q_577415821", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 26}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "春节去国外旅行有哪些攻略分享？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-4d0028ee64b0b4071bb3f9c93b22e0a2_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "l